text: Theresa Matauaina Fitzpatrick (born 25 February 1995) is a New Zealand rugby union player. Fitzpatrick undertakes medical studies at the University of Auckland. She represents New Zealand in rugby sevens. She made her sevens debut at the 2016 USA Women's Sevens. She was named in the sevens squad for the 2016 Summer Olympics. Fitzpatrick is the younger sister of former Silver Fern and Samoan sevens player Sulu Tone-Fitzpatrick.
